content:
📅 Event Period: September 26, 2025, 14:00 (UTC) - October 3, 2025, 23:59 (UTC)
👥 Eligible Participants: Users must complete mobile phone verification to register
During the event, new and existing users who complete the net deposit and trading requirements can claim up to 2000 USDT in XPL/USDT free contract positions!
Net Deposit = Total Deposit - Total Withdrawals (any blockchain deposit of any coin). Users can deposit any equivalent asset.
Trading Volume: All USDT-margin contract volume.
Eligible users must meet both the net deposit and trading volume requirements to unlock reward levels. Each user can unlock only one reward level, based on the highest standards achieved during the event period.
Event Rules:
1. Users must actively click “Join Now” on the page to participate in the event;
2. Each account can only join one promotion event of the same type within the same period;
3. Rewards will be distributed within five business days after the event ends;
4. Free positions will be distributed as position airdrop vouchers, and reward usage rules are governed by the Terms and Conditions in the Rewards Hub;
5. Market makers, API traders, and institutional accounts are not eligible for this event;
6. Zoomex reserves the right to cancel the participation of users who engage in malicious activities to gain profit, such as creating multiple accounts to obtain additional rewards or other illegal, fraudulent, or harmful actions;
7. Zoomex reserves the final interpretation rights for this event.

To attract top traders to join Zoomex, we’re launching the “Zero-Fee Copy Trading Program”!
From now on, become a trader and complete copy trading tasks to enjoy 100% fee rebates on copy trades — up to 1,000 USDT cashback!
Join Zoomex as a trader and earn profits with zero trading cost!
⏰Event Period: June 20, 2025 10:00 (UTC) – August 20, 2025 10:00 (UTC)
🌟 Task Details
Task	Beginner Task (within 7 days)	Advanced Task (within 14 days)	Elite Task (within 30 days)
Copy Trading Days	≥ 3 days	≥ 7 days	≥ 15 days
Daily Followers	≥ 5 users	≥ 10 users	≥ 20 users
7-Day ROI	≥ 5%	≥ 10%	≥ 20%
Copy Trading Volume	≥ 20,000 USDT	≥ 100,000 USDT	≥ 1,000,000 USDT
Fee Rebate	Up to 100 USDT	Up to 500 USDT	Up to 1,000 USDT
About Copy Trading on Zoomex
Zoomex currently has 90,000+ copy trading users and over 2.8 million in follower profits. Traders can earn up to 40% commission rebates, and top performers receive homepage promotion and exposure across Zoomex official channels.Join now and start your journey as a star trader!
Event Rules
1,Users must click the “Join Now” button to participate;
2,Fee rebates are equivalent to the actual fees paid by the user and will be distributed in USDT to the funding account;
3,Daily follower count refers to the number of users copying the trader during task days. Days with less than the required follower count will be considered invalid;
4,Copy trading volume refers to the total trading volume of all followers during the task period;
5,ROI and volume stats are based on platform data. Wash trading or malicious activity is strictly prohibited;
6,Platform staff will review results within 7 working days after task completion. Rebates will be issued in USDT to the user’s funding account;
7,Users can complete multiple tasks during the event. However, the total rebate amount will not exceed the actual fees paid;
8,Zoomex reserves the right to disqualify users engaging in malicious behavior, including but not limited to creating multiple accounts to claim extra rewards or any fraudulent/abusive behavior;
9,Zoomex reserves the final interpretation rights for this campaign.
